'''佛祖機場'''（{{lang-ne|गौतम बुद्ध विमानस्थल}}，{{airport codes|BWA|VNBW}}），是一個位於尼泊爾[[錫陀塔那迦|錫陀塔那迦]]的[[國內機場|國內機場]]<ref name="GCM" />，同時作為[[藍毗尼省|藍毗尼省]][[藍毗尼|藍毗尼]]的樞紐機場。目前正在擴建成[[國際機場|國際機場]]，預計2020年12月完工<ref>{{Cite web|title=Tourism Ministry drops plan to name Munich Airport as operator of Bhairahawa airport|url=https://kathmandupost.com/money/2020/07/15/tourism-ministry-drops-plan-to-name-munich-airport-as-operator-of-bhairahawa-airport|access-date=2020-07-17|website=kathmandupost.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200906152032/https://kathmandupost.com/money/2020/07/15/tourism-ministry-drops-plan-to-name-munich-airport-as-operator-of-bhairahawa-airport|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=BD |first1=Dipen |title=Gautam Buddha International Airport Due to Open Near Lumbini, Nepal, in Mid-2020 |url=https://www.buddhistdoor.net/news/gautam-buddha-international-airport-due-to-open-near-lumbini-nepal-in-mid-2020 |accessdate=4 March 2020 |agency=buddhistdoor |date=2019-12-06 |ref=government target of commencing operations in mid-2020 |archive-date=2020-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920044953/https://www.buddhistdoor.net/news/gautam-buddha-international-airport-due-to-open-near-lumbini-nepal-in-mid-2020 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此機場將成為尼泊爾第二個國際機場。

